{"featured_counts":1,"common_counts":37,"collapsed_counts":0,"reviewing_counts":0,"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/562357157/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=7\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/answers/562357157/root_comments?include=data%5B%2A%5D.author%2Ccollapsed%2Creply_to_author%2Cdisliked%2Ccontent%2Cvoting%2Cvote_count%2Cis_parent_author%2Cis_author\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=5\u0026order=normal\u0026status=open","totals":12},"data":[{"id":567613271,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567613271","content":"还有人不理解，我就说的再稍显一点。火发明之前，人类几百年来对大型野兽也基本毫无办法。偶尔出来一个基因完美，体力超群，训练有素的陈氏高手千辛万苦打跑了豹子，世上仅此一人，然后陈氏断言普通人不可能打跑狮子，不要去尝试这种送命的事情，直到一个高中生无意中发现了钻木起火，一个大火炬把狮子吓得屁滚尿流。你看，几千年多少人在研究怎么搞定大型野兽，结果都没能成功，那这能说明钻木起火很难嘛？陈氏说的有错吗，没错。但是，一旦你的思路陷入了肉搏这个死胡同，也许会越走越远。那么哥猜呢，是不是也陷入了复杂方法这个死胡同？","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546128596,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"47d7fa6a97290bbaaadefe248a6a4fdd","url_token":"xie-qiu-chen-99","name":"小小晓芾","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac10fdc9a63dbd077e44a58e9c5c4dd4_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac10fdc9a63dbd077e44a58e9c5c4dd4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/47d7fa6a97290bbaaadefe248a6a4fdd","user_type":"people","headline":"精通城市规划，房地产发展","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0,"child_comment_count":5,"child_comments":[{"id":567629247,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567629247","content":"完全错误的例子。\u003cbr\u003e首先从这个例子中可以看出您的核心问题是以为初等数学还能挖到大宝藏？当然也不必拘泥于初等数学，也可能是这个高中生自学了高等数学然后发现了大宝藏？那这个就是最基本的认识问题了，或许讨论下去也没有什么意义了。\u003cbr\u003e我只能说，做数学的不是一群庸才，相反是最富有灵感和洞见力的一群人，数学早就过了“发明钻木取火”的时代，那是魏尔斯特拉斯、黎曼、阿贝尔们干的事情，现在相当于人们造出了内燃机，现在有人研究风能、水能，有人研究核能，有人努力钻研受控核聚变，结果突然冒出一个人宣布造出了永动机，永远解决了能源问题？？或者说，您的意思是有一种特殊能源人们还没有发现，发现了就能瞬间解决能源问题？\u003cbr\u003e举的陈景润的例子也是相当可笑。如果把智力比作武力，哥猜是一个怪兽，用初等数学证明哥猜就相当于一个人赤手空拳打了很久，发现怪兽一滴血都没掉。而现代数学早就不是肉搏战，而是使用各种先进武器。人们用这些先进武器，发现可以使怪兽不断掉血。陈景润相当于一个武力超群的人，在使用前人发明的激光炮、导弹的基础上，自己造出了高达，终于使怪兽掉到半血以下，在这种情况下，他说：赤手空拳打死怪兽是有可能的，但是近期内一个人体力再强，也不太可能找到赤手空拳打死怪兽的方法，这有什么问题吗？\u003cbr\u003e另外，“哥猜是不是也陷入了复杂方法这个死胡同？”，这个金句简直承包了我一天的笑点。\u003cbr\u003e你们看着人们不断摆弄长枪短炮试图攻击怪兽，觉得这样好傻，为什么不直接上去肉搏呢？也许正有一套少林组合拳，三下两下就把怪兽干倒了。\u003cbr\u003e你们到底对数学有什么样的误解呀？？","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546132394,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"8aff271b5a6de5de9fec6b29b1253bdf","url_token":"huang-yu-zhu-38-10","name":"黄毓宁","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46a928dacb166c66e406cdb2146474a8_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46a928dacb166c66e406cdb2146474a8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/8aff271b5a6de5de9fec6b29b1253bdf","user_type":"people","headline":"水货大学生/期待为科学奋斗/LGBT","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":3,"reply_to_author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"47d7fa6a97290bbaaadefe248a6a4fdd","url_token":"xie-qiu-chen-99","name":"小小晓芾","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac10fdc9a63dbd077e44a58e9c5c4dd4_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac10fdc9a63dbd077e44a58e9c5c4dd4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/47d7fa6a97290bbaaadefe248a6a4fdd","user_type":"people","headline":"精通城市规划，房地产发展","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0},{"id":567633242,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567633242","content":"我并没有说只能用现在的初等数学去解决哥猜啊。你也明白，简单的方法跟初等数学不等价。简单的方法可以是一个全新的方法，不一定是现有的初等高等数学。哥猜不能用初等数学解决，不等于不能用其他全新的体系去解决。另外你说现在的武器已经很高级了那没错，但是很难有发展了，我不能苟同，高达，核武器是很厉害，但是你过几百年再来看看，也许这些就跟古代的木棍一样弱智。每个时期的人都会觉得现在的科技比以前强很多了，很难爆发性增长了，但是人类的发展后，都是对这个结论啪啪打脸的。人类诞生了500万年了，研究一直在加速，你又怎么能断言我们这100年就恰好到了最强的时候很难发展了呢","featured":false,"collapsed":false,"is_author":false,"is_delete":false,"created_time":1546133145,"resource_type":"answer","reviewing":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"allow_reply":true,"allow_vote":true,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"author":{"role":"author","member":{"id":"47d7fa6a97290bbaaadefe248a6a4fdd","url_token":"xie-qiu-chen-99","name":"小小晓芾","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac10fdc9a63dbd077e44a58e9c5c4dd4_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac10fdc9a63dbd077e44a58e9c5c4dd4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/47d7fa6a97290bbaaadefe248a6a4fdd","user_type":"people","headline":"精通城市规划，房地产发展","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false}},"vote_count":0,"reply_to_author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"8aff271b5a6de5de9fec6b29b1253bdf","url_token":"huang-yu-zhu-38-10","name":"黄毓宁","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46a928dacb166c66e406cdb2146474a8_r.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-46a928dacb166c66e406cdb2146474a8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/8aff271b5a6de5de9fec6b29b1253bdf","user_type":"people","headline":"水货大学生/期待为科学奋斗/LGBT","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false}},"voting":false,"disliked":false,"censor_status":0}]}]}
